onno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔記左得邊個左軚地方可以</blockquote><br />\n一樣要綠燈先轉得<br />\n但綠燈轉右時，右邊既斑馬線亦有機會係綠，要讓左行人先"},{"pid":"59e865b749d53ffe21910dc78f1f2d7a12a6b63b","tid":218264,"uid":73677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>紅燈可以右轉，不過要讓行人。<br />\n小心電單車</blockquote><br />\n邊個話紅燈可以右轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔記左得邊個左軚地方可以</blockquote><br />\n一樣要綠燈先轉得<br />\n但綠燈轉右時，右邊既斑馬線亦有機會係綠，要讓左行人先</blockquote><br />\n佢當台灣係大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129f6135da34031d67ed8f6150481a40c8e80310","tid":218264,"uid":24682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:52:56.000Z","msg":"要注意右手邊長期好多電單車<br />\n紅綠燈位行人路前有電單車既待轉區<br />\n所以燈位起步睇完行人再睇下電單車先好行"}]}